    "Koç-Koç": "The coming together of two fire energies creates an explosion of sparks in the first seconds of the relationship. Since you are each other's mirror, you understand best the other party's need for independence and impatience; However, this situation can sometimes turn into an ego war. Your approaches to life are so similar that when you are together, you present a fearless front to the world. However, you may both need to slow down a bit to move from saying 'I' to 'we'. This dynamic heralds a beginning where passion never ends but the struggle for leadership is always action-packed.",
