    "Koç-Yay": "Your life energy is so high and harmonious that you are like two different passengers of the same soul. The desire to explore and passion for freedom of both signs will make you rush towards common goals from the first days of the relationship. The optimistic and courageous attitude you display towards life when you are together turns into an inspiring source of joy for the people around you. Even your arguments are usually like philosophical debates, and you quickly find a solution and move on, without holding a grudge. This relationship is one of the most enjoyable gifts the universe offers you, where there are no restrictions and every moment is experienced as a celebration.",
    "Koç-Oğlak": "Aries' childish enthusiasm and Capricorn's mature and dignified stance can initially create a serious distance between your two selves. This fundamental difference in your approach to life can make Aries seem too impatient and Capricorn too distant and prescriptive. Since you are both cardinal signs, it is inevitable that you will enter into a silent but deep competition over who will rule. But this duo has the potential to be an incredibly successful 'power couple', with one providing the energy and the other setting the strategy. When you respect each other's boundaries, Aries' fire will warm Capricorn's cold discipline and a very solid future will emerge.",
