    "Koç-Balık": "When the first and last signs of the zodiac meet, a mystical cycle occurs in your perspective on life. When the concrete energy with which Aries dives into the world is combined with the dreamer and spiritual depth of Pisces, a somewhat complex but fascinating picture emerges. While Aries acts with the instinct to protect Pisces' fragility; Pisces softens Aries' harsh corners and gives him a more compassionate perspective. But Aries' directness can sometimes hurt Pisces' sensitive soul, or Pisces' indecisiveness can infuriate Aries. If you can build this delicate bridge between the ego and the soul, you can open the doors of worlds you have never known to each other.",
