    "Boğa-Yengeç": "Your approach to life is so harmonious that from the first moment you may feel as if you have known each other for many years. You both value safety, belonging, and a peaceful life above all else; This creates a great synchronization in the House of Self. When Cancer's emotional sensitivity combines with Taurus' protective and calm attitude, a very compassionate relationship emerges. To those around you, you portray an image of a couple that is extremely warm, inviting and connected to their roots. This natural flow between you is based on nurturing each other rather than conflict. This is an extremely nourishing beginning where the soul and body find peace in the same harbor.",
