    "Aslan-Aslan": "The meeting of two Leo energies in your vision house allows you to build your life philosophy on a monument of success and pride. When together, you display an unwavering self-confidence towards life and defend your common ideals with great passion and generosity. Being very determined and 'noble' about your beliefs will enable you to become an authority figure that is admired by those around you. Your distant travels are always based on the most glittering, highest quality and prestigious experiences that will make you feel like a king/queen. Higher education processes that bring academic success and social prestige are your main source of motivation that nourishes your vision. This bond is a magnificent future plan, every moment of which is bright, joyful and crowned with unshakable faith, like two suns looking at the same horizon.",
