    "Aslan-Başak": "In your social life, Leo's visionary shine and Virgo's meticulous organizational ability create a tremendous balance. While Leo stands out in your circle of friends with his creative ideas and charisma, Virgo analyzes how productive these social relationships are and quietly plans all the necessary details for your common ideals. In your hopes for the future, both the desire to achieve great prestige and the desire to be useful to society are intertwined. Honesty and helpfulness are at the forefront in your friendships; You are known around you as a couple who 'thinks about everything down to the smallest detail and achieves great results'. However, when Leo's exaggerated social plans hit Virgo's critical filter, sometimes annoying little arguments may occur. When one party's energy combines with the other party's discipline, you build a very solid companionship that turns your dreams into reality, step by step.",
